Package: hydeR
Type: Package
Title: R functions for Hyde High School
Version: 0.7.4
Authors@R: person("Afsar", "Chowdhury", email = "a.chowdhury@hydehighschool.uk",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Afsar Chowdhury <a.chowdhury@hydehighschool.uk>
Description: R funnctions for Hyde High School.
    The package makes extensive use of g4sr, an API wrapper for Go4Schools.
    Authentication is required for all g4sr requests.  See your school's 
    administrator for an API key.
